Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有在深刻地反省
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:03.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反省什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒忍住吃掉了儲備的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作為自發的懲罰
