Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:04:02.63,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}3天2晚  伊豆之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸之前也拿到抽獎券了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要去試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是頭獎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:15.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以和寵物一起溫泉旅行的三天兩晚的旅行券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恭喜您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這兒  是人氣旅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克也能一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H565551&\frx18\fry356\frz16.78\pos(896,188.8)\org(897.6,259.2)}和寵物一起溫泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H565551&\frx8\fry0\frz17.71\pos(1048,636.8)\org(1054.4,705.6)}使用期限  1月6日~1月末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord2\c&H565551&\fscx91\fscy97\frz17.66\frx6\fry358\pos(1116.8,945.6)\org(1155.2,1011.2)}※需要預約  {\fs50}使用本券時請務必提前與我們聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論如何都得在年內幹完7號刊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是一旦下定決心就一定會做到的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是老師  好漢該出手時就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已確認收下7號刊的原稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我預約了要去夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以還在擔心要是完不成該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.10,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僵住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,夏威夷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,三個月之前就預約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還真是讓人捏了一把汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那時候我還沒給你說過要畫七號刊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我覺得您多半會畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種事情早點講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為要是講了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定就會故意不畫讓我去不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人類還沒有墮落到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:23.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聽了這事後幹勁低落最終導致畫不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這期間我也要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師也要去旅行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以呢  是要去哪兒旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆  挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過我是去夏威夷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是這種地方會讓人幹勁低落的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為啥  我的確是要去夏威夷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,相較於漫畫家拚命換來的假期  3天2晚的小旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&HE45458&\frz18.8\pos(592,244.8)}箱根溫泉\N\h{\fs40}2天1晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\pos(1190.667,420.8)\frz296.8\c&H7067CB&}熱海旅行  3天2晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H2024AD&\frz82.51\pos(1246.933,318.933)}親子溫泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.83,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz343.9\pos(681.333,433.334)\c&H60C5E7&}當日回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙隨隨便便就是去海外度假一週
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H39CDE3&\3c&H000000&\move(89.6,219.2,308.4,220.8,0,2859)}泰國曼谷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H71EFF6&\3c&H2B6B55&\frz31.55\move(408,785.6,631.2,782,0,2859)}夏威夷火奴魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.96,kakushigoto in 12,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz340.2\c&H44C4D5&\3c&H1F1610&\move(992,334.4,1201.6,337.6,0,2859)}瑞士{\c&H4A34CD&}阿爾卑斯{\c&HFFFFFF&}之旅  {\c&HF3E9E5&}5天6晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿也完成了  假期也有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對漫畫家來說  預定長期旅行是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道會不會因為什麼麻煩導致原稿畫不完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz18.5\pos(267.2,148.8)\c&H3C3948&}隨身帶美工刀被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(1118.4,48)}助手逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(272,904)\frz8.946}沉迷動森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\frz6.601\pos(681.6,681.6)}座椅彈簧跳出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.39,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H3C3948&\pos(1169.6,736)}因为打雷使工作地點停電
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便在年內畫好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1088,208)}啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz278.3\pos(518.4,212.8)}這個拿去改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卡在明年初的終審需要重交的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還必須要從旅行的地方回來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特別是黃段子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以只有能馬上回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「安·近·短」的選項
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.44,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：安在日語中有便宜的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在跨年時期去海外度假的漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都是垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且  漫畫家在跨年時期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能隨便制定計劃最大的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,必然會得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真會說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放假把一年份的病都給消化了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿攢不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,病倒是攢起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明職場慶功宴都還沒舉辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,職場上的人員在這兒我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但為什麼你們也在這兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,普通地來探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,布丁的話吃得下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事  課長只是單純的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  部長只是單純的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們先統一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別擔心  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,旅行之前我一定會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,旅行是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抽獎中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來是這麼回事麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,伊豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且還帶螃蟹自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.31,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs65\c&HCA7DE2&\3c&H411EB6&\frz21.21\pos(380.8,403.2)}和寵物一起{\c&H5777E3&}温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.31,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H3B15CA&\frz30.95\pos(1513.6,793.6)}螃蟹{\c&H2F2C48&\bord0}自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,螃蟹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:48.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道是因為姬寫了很多「蟹」字才中獎的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,寫願望原來有效果的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是像吸引法則一樣的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了  為了讓孩子他爸早點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家一起來寫願望祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要寫什麼字比較好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要寫願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抄經文不是挺好的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:18.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了  從編輯部回來後就來晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這熟人滿聚一堂的感覺是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說老師他…病危了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,經…經文？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您要去世了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去世？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為病危才會聚了這麼多人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼…原來我是病危啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呀  經文這不都給準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是大家  都說只是單純的感冒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會對本人說出真相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您快掛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…你給我適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,死而復生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬要是當真了該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師  還不能勉強起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請不要亂來啊老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,死雖然是死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是可能要休刊一次左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到那時候就說「作者去取材了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「作者犯死罪了」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論如何都想要一死麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎  在姬面前說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  她似乎因為擔心而累倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,燒也基本上退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因為抄經文起效了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然寫願望挺靈的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺已經好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,病已經好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  燒也退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能按計劃去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然寫願望挺靈的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,寫願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}要結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,結婚成就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.09,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}脫單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,寫願望真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這是詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被思慕的人也挺可憐的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:32.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,靠著抽獎中的旅行券  我們正在前往溫泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直都挺在意一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父親和女兒的二人旅行  會被人怎麼看待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.25,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H62676B&\pos(313.6,382.4)}小汪之家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恭候已久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生  請問是三位麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  是兩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  是三人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz284.4\move(1273.6,417.6,1275,358)}洛克？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是三人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼  這種地方狗也要算一人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還以為是以媽媽在為前提問的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能帶狗狗住的和式房間真是少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是這家旅店的特色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然我們對溫泉也很有自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被稱作是德川家的隱藏溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隱藏溫泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隱藏溫泉是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是不會被其他人找到的而隱藏的溫泉…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:39.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要藏著  讓大家都泡泡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  溫泉旅館給人一種「隱瞞之事」很多的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正如  婚外戀的幽會場所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或是政治家躲避媒體的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.27,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(871.6,762.6)}客房負責人  莎拉波娃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或者是不要詢問工作人員的過往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:12:00.40,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}莎拉波娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  不要叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這裡你要做一個紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許是隔壁房間也有狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.04,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1459.2,244.8)}正在改裝中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又或是出過事的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:29.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,溫泉  溫泉  吃飯之前泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我稍微有些擔心溫泉浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓她一個人的話我很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但一起的話我更擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是想稍微看下她的情況我就會被立即逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種時候我到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如此為女兒著想的我  怎麼可能沒預料到這種情況會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:51.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真沒想到你會把我們叫來女浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠免費來泡溫泉倒是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但您為什麼這麼擔心泡溫泉這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你知道有多少日本人是死在泡溫泉的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且  還有那些可惡漫畫家畫的溫泉段子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我全是些不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜託了  幫我照看好姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是發生了什麼  我們會立即通知您的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒…姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:23.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我泡得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你已經泡好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我有些擔心洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你慢慢泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不來偷窺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們可都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要再說這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.22,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(955.2,265.6)}正在改裝中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然很讓人在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.98,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry14\frz269.1\pos(176,496)\org(448,571.2)}正在改裝中  不可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這間房間是不是什麼出過事的禁忌房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們正準備將其改造成展示室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,展示室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡曾是文豪田端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.82,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自現實文豪川端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,寫出「伊豆的羅勒」的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.70,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自川端康成所著「伊豆的舞女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:11.74,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,0)\fs45\frz299\c&H65748D&\move(480,166.4,641.2,150.4,0,6572)}不是芥末  而是羅勒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來就是在這個房間寫出那部名作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,螃蟹  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這間旅館總感覺背後隱藏著好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已經不想再繼續隱瞞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我會向我老婆坦白然後離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和你正大光明地結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這個真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他是因為料理太過好吃深受感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  蛭賀尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我也有隱瞞著的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我其實並不是26歲而是40歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且還離了兩次婚欠了500萬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  謝謝你告訴我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也隱瞞了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你生日時我送給你的這隻狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實並不是吉娃娃而是雜種狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吉娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我已經唯它不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,品種什麼的怎麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是謝謝你能夠告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠說出來  我也覺得輕鬆了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,任何狗狗都很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是  我反對犬種歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我對老婆你也有隱瞞之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:37.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我也隱瞞著我早就發現你隱瞞著的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:40.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在時機正好  將自己的隱瞞之事說出來會很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我已經被裁員了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我每天都裝作去上班其實都是在公園裡打發時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實住宿這間旅館的錢我用的是公款  而我卻隱瞞了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我的眼睛  鼻子  嘴巴和下巴都是整容過的  而我卻隱瞞著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實大家剛才吃的伊豆高原牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是從我聽也沒聽過的國家進口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這什麼情節展開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來輪到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  我並沒有什麼隱瞞之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:21.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來吧  將你的隱瞞之事說出來  和我們一起輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:25.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來一同解脫吧  將隱瞞之事捨去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:30.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}來吧  來吧  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這協同的壓迫感究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:36.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}來吧  來吧  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的隱瞞之事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,房間裡好像有什麼黑影在動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不想再隱瞞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實  這間房間裡有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會出現田端康成老師的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:13.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每晚都在寫著未完結的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說出來  我也痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有隱瞞之事真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,730.6)}客房負責人  莎拉波娃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:26.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你的莎拉波娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了  田端康成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在旅館寫作時突然吐血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,之後在醫院去世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吐血和殉情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前文豪們的故事都挺有戲劇色彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且人物形象也都挺鮮明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像這樣作者的鮮明特點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是造就了作品的評價的一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果我也吐血  是不是我的漫畫就能賣出去更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:54.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黃段子漫畫家吐血也只會被恥笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,基本上像吐血這樣正經的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對搞笑漫畫家來說是負面影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀者可就笑不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  您用您的裸照塑造自己的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也是一種對真相的偽裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起  只是我的想像而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不然你也不會做那麼蠢的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你真是說得好讓人傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,噓  你會吵醒姬的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能去那裡  洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是洛克被帶到魔界了  姬會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有鬼  沒有鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麝香貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來這傢伙就是文豪的真面目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,布置還是和當初一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是在這張書桌前完成了那部名作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是真有文豪的鬼魂的話  我倒是想被它附上身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,保佑我成為人氣漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就這麼一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個時間應該不會被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你個笨蛋  怎麼可能有幽靈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有很多人看見過的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我絕對要拍到幽靈的照片  然後拿到很多讚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:30.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是那間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:41.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看  見  了  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聽說昨晚幽靈出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  早晨這件事就鬧得挺厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬你不怕幽靈之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我當然也很怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:04.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我想如果他們能夠存在的話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果在的話  幽靈的數量就會很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實  如果死去的人都變成了幽靈  那數量就很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,地球可就裝不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:22.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以它們才是透明的  和它們撞上也能穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能夠觸碰它們也是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看  前段時間的旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A5E59&\bord2\frx10\fry0\org(105.6,372.8)\pos(321.6,340.8)\frz20.28}出現了？文豪幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx10\fry0\frz20.28\pos(443.2,553.6)\org(227.2,585.6)}由加里的旅館疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx10\fry0\frz24.02\pos(992,944)\org(776,976)}附近學生所拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H7A5E59&\frx8\fry358\frz24.82\pos(1153.6,956.8)\org(1115.2,982.4)}「小汪之家」出現幽靈騷動就在旅館附近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的超可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過這個文豪幽靈身上沒什麼氣場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.30,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(1665.6,390.4)\frz273.7\c&HAD93FF&\3c&H7E3FDF&}點讚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父親他有這麼一個習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每每遇到討厭和煩惱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他總會從外廊進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那天父親回來後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了不讓我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是自己工作能力提高了  被別家公司挖過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有了一份更好的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我察覺到了那是他自己辭去了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那時他辭去的原來就是這份畫畫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼他不願意繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然他本人寫的是賣不出去了不想繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但你也知道並不是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是他自己不願意再動筆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣說  聽上去比較帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實他是畫不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師也對讀者有著隱瞞之事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為他無論怎麼畫都不能讓讀者笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這事你也不用專門說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師又沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:51.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但將作者和作品分開來看待的人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:52.28,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz350.4\pos(160,73.6)\3c&H30323F&}8人失蹤。持續搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:52.28,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz351.9\pos(1017.6,224)\3c&H2D303D&}事故現場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,悲慘的私生活被人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對搞笑漫畫家來說是致命傷
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
