Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,風之緊身褲還有十週就將完結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我原以為這樣的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:41.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠一直持續下去
